<li><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: medium;">第3課題：木造住宅(２)断面詳細図</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: medium;">第4課題：RC造</span></li>
